Deploying the pear.unl.edu website
============================================

Prerequisites
-------------
The developer needs a SSH account on `pear.unl.edu` and
has to be in the `ucomm` group.


Local setup
-----------
::

$ git remote add live ssh://pear.unl.edu/Library/WebServer/pear.unl.edu

Deployment
----------
::

$ git push live master
